    "enclosingTopic": "Binyan",
    "enclosingSubtopic": "A shoresh is put \"into\" a binyan to produce a word"
   },
   {
    "text": " represents a vague and general category of meaning, putting that shoresh into a particular ",
    "type": "text"
   },
   {
