   {
    "text": " would produce a more specific verb or adjective. For example, the shoresh אבל corresponds to the general idea of eating, whereas putting that shoresh into a particular binyan might produce the specific verbs לֶאֱכוֹל \"to eat,\" לְהַאֲכִיל \"to feed,\" or adjective אָכוּל \"eaten.\"",
    "type": "text"
   }
  ]
